http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/andhra-pradesh/%E2%80%9CStudy-on-China%E2%80%99s-growth-engines-will-help-State%E2%80%9D/article13978514.ece

“Study on China’s growth will help State”Secretary to Higher Education Department and author of the ‘China: Behind the Miracle, Sumita Dawra on Saturday said that there was a need of a deep understanding on the growth engines of China as people of Andhra Pradesh were in a crucial period of building their dream capital. Speaking on the sidelines of her recent visit to Krishna University, Ms. Dawara said that she strongly believed that the China models of economy would certainly help Andhra Pradesh achieve its targeted goals on various fronts. She presented a copy of her book to Chief Minister N. Chandrababu Naidu last week.